listings_desc:
Description
A Modern Double-Story Terrace Houses
                                    Acacia Park is a project of landed properties in the form of terrace homes. Located in the Rawang township and is the product of the Low Yat Group.

Aside from the school located within the neighbourhood, there are numerous other education facilities in the vicinity including Sekolah Integrasi Tasik Puteri and Universiti Selangor (UNISEL). Popular supermarket chains such as AEON Rawang and Tesco Rawang are within a stone’s throw from home at about 10 minutes away by car. There is also the Sungai Buloh Hospital located about 25 minute’s drive away.

Getting onto the Guthrie Corridor Expressway (GCE) is seamless, providing residents with easy access to Shah Alam. There is also the Kuala Lumpur-Kuala Selangor Expressway (LATAR) where residents will find that getting to either Kuala Lumpur or Kuala Selangor is highly convenient. The North-South Expressway (PLUS) is equally accessible from the neighbourhood, providing access to the other states.

The homes at Acacia Park are highly affordable for the middle-income group, where buyers are able to purchase leasehold double-storey homes for less than the RM500,000 mark.

Description
Kota Kemuning Bayu 24x75
                                    Kota Kemuning Bayu 2 Storey 24x75 Nice House,Well Maintain,Move-in condition For 850K/Please Call Raymond Cheah 012-6897155 


Kemuning Bayu is an affluent freehold neighbourhood in the township of Kemuning Utama, Shah Alam Selangor. Kemuning Bayu is one of the largest precincts within this township with some 879 residential units. These freehold double-storey terrace houses are built by its developer Paramount Property, a diversified listed Malaysian conglomerate. Kemuning Bayu neighbors the equally affluent Kota Kemuning township. This gated and guarded neighborhood is a highly popular residential development as it offers easy access to major highways.

Kemuning Bayu is a well-planned neighborhood offering ample outdoor facilities and promotes outdoor activities.
Kemuning Bayu Accessibility And Amenities
One advantage of Kemuning Bayu is that is easily accessible via the Shah Alam Expressway (KESAS), Kemuning-Shah Alam Expressway and ELITE Highway making travel hassle-free. There are also buses and taxis that you can take to reach Kemuning Bayu.

A host of amenities nearby Kemuning Bayu are available for residents conveniences such as SJK (T ) Taman Ladang Emerald, SJK (C ) Khe Beng and SK Bukit Kemuning within close proximity whilst for groceries and fresh produce residents can head to Econsave, Pasar Tani Kota Kemuning, Yeon Market Enterprise and Giant Kemuning Utama. For shopping the nearest mall would be neighbouring Gamuda Walk Mall, further away there is Main Place Mall, One City Mall, Setia City Mall and SACC Mall, amongst others. For medical emergencies, Columbia Hospital Bukit Rimau is just a short drive away. Residents would not have to go too far for food as there are plenty of options within close distance of their residences, Bigg Boss Curry House, Selasih Kasturi, Bean Garden and Restaurant KK Corner are some of them.

Kindly Please Call Raymond Cheah For More unit Information 012-6897155

name: The Pulse
address: Jalan Puteri 7/13, Bandar Puteri Puchong, Puchong, Selangor
listings_desc:
Description
Great community, near to LRT Station & Business Hub
                                    The Pulse Residence is a freehold high-rise serviced residence located in Bandar Puteri Puchong, Selangor. Situated along Lebuh Puteri. The Pulse Residence is set amidst lush foliage and abundant greenery, built to cater to its dwellers’ needs of community, safety, accessibility, education and well-being in mind.

Thoughtfully designed, the development is to meet the modern-day needs with its contemporary design and practical spaces. The Pulse Residence is made up of two 44-storey buildings, with a total of 579 serviced apartments within.

There are also 21 units of retail shops scattered across 3 floors of retail podiums. Meanwhile, the residential units here range between 818 sf to 1,851 sf, offering layouts from 2 to 4+1 bedrooms and 2 to 3 bathrooms.

This freehold development will offer residents over 30 recreational and social facilities, some of which include a parcourse, children’s playground, half basketball court, multipurpose hall, swimming pool, barbeque deck, reading corner and a lounge.

Upon completion, The Pulse Residence will be greeted with easy access and connectivity to major locales such as Kuala Lumpur, Petaling Jaya, Shah Alam, Klang, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, and KLIA via an extensive network of highways.

The major thoroughfares mentioned above include the Damansara Puchong Highway (LDP), Shah Alam Highway (KESAS), South Klang Valley Expressway (SKVE), Elite Highway, Federal Highway and Maju Expressway (MEX).

Located in Bandar Puteri Puchong, The Pulse Residence is surrounded by a myriad of conveniences. Just right next to the development is the Columbia Asia Hospital, and slightly further away are The Cube commercial area, Four Points by Sheraton Puchong, Puchong Financial Corporate Center (PFCC) and IOI Mall, just to name a few.

Description
Great view & superb facilities
                                    Sky Condominium is a luxurious high rise development located at 200 meters above sea level in Bandar Puchong Jaya. Uniquely designed as a resort-style condominium with an environmentally friendly surrounding,Sky Condominium comes complete with lush greenery and excellent connectivity, offering investors and property buyers a reason for investment and purchase thanks to the property's prime address and its high quality living experience.

Sky Condominium is designed to be bungalows in the sky with their spacious built-ups. These family-centric homes aresized at between 1,173 sf and 1,658 sf with a minimum of three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The density here is of moderate proportions, with a total of 1041 units spread out over five blocks. The density is however not very heavily felt with the spaciousness of the development.

Residents of Sky Condominium will be pampered with the best of facilities with no overcrowding despite having five blocks of residences. There will be 14 sky lounges to cater to every resident and 3 themed podium gardens. The Swimming pool is also vastly sized at 1.5 times the size of a typical Olympic pool.Security at Sky Condominium will be very tight with the 6-tier security system. There will be 24-hour CCTVsurveillance at blind spots and all areas, with an access card required for access to every part of the building. The Building will also have integrated panic buttons for emergencies.

In terms of transportation, there are a myriad of highways that residents can get to quickly and conveniently. The ShahAlam Expressway (KESAS) is nearby as is the Damansara-Puchong Highway (LDP). By utilizing these roads, getting to Bandar Sunway and Shah Alam is very convenient.The closest LRT train station is only 10 minutes away from Sky Condominium, and bus and taxi terminals are only 5minutes away. For amenities there is the Puchong town center which has every bank conceivable, and there is also theIOI Shopping Mall for entertainment.

name: The Pulse
address: Jalan Puteri 7/13, Bandar Puteri Puchong, Puchong, Selangor
listings_desc:
Description
Great community, near to LRT Station & Business Hub
                                    The Pulse Residence is a freehold high-rise serviced residence located in Bandar Puteri Puchong, Selangor. Situated along Lebuh Puteri. The Pulse Residence is set amidst lush foliage and abundant greenery, built to cater to its dwellers’ needs of community, safety, accessibility, education and well-being in mind.

Thoughtfully designed, the development is to meet the modern-day needs with its contemporary design and practical spaces. The Pulse Residence is made up of two 44-storey buildings, with a total of 579 serviced apartments within.

There are also 21 units of retail shops scattered across 3 floors of retail podiums. Meanwhile, the residential units here range between 818 sf to 1,851 sf, offering layouts from 2 to 4+1 bedrooms and 2 to 3 bathrooms.

This freehold development will offer residents over 30 recreational and social facilities, some of which include a parcourse, children’s playground, half basketball court, multipurpose hall, swimming pool, barbeque deck, reading corner and a lounge.

Upon completion, The Pulse Residence will be greeted with easy access and connectivity to major locales such as Kuala Lumpur, Petaling Jaya, Shah Alam, Klang, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, and KLIA via an extensive network of highways.

The major thoroughfares mentioned above include the Damansara Puchong Highway (LDP), Shah Alam Highway (KESAS), South Klang Valley Expressway (SKVE), Elite Highway, Federal Highway and Maju Expressway (MEX).

Located in Bandar Puteri Puchong, The Pulse Residence is surrounded by a myriad of conveniences. Just right next to the development is the Columbia Asia Hospital, and slightly further away are The Cube commercial area, Four Points by Sheraton Puchong, Puchong Financial Corporate Center (PFCC) and IOI Mall, just to name a few.

Description
A Modern Double-Story Terrace Houses
                                    Acacia Park is a project of landed properties in the form of terrace homes. Located in the Rawang township and is the product of the Low Yat Group.

Aside from the school located within the neighbourhood, there are numerous other education facilities in the vicinity including Sekolah Integrasi Tasik Puteri and Universiti Selangor (UNISEL). Popular supermarket chains such as AEON Rawang and Tesco Rawang are within a stone’s throw from home at about 10 minutes away by car. There is also the Sungai Buloh Hospital located about 25 minute’s drive away.

Getting onto the Guthrie Corridor Expressway (GCE) is seamless, providing residents with easy access to Shah Alam. There is also the Kuala Lumpur-Kuala Selangor Expressway (LATAR) where residents will find that getting to either Kuala Lumpur or Kuala Selangor is highly convenient. The North-South Expressway (PLUS) is equally accessible from the neighbourhood, providing access to the other states.

The homes at Acacia Park are highly affordable for the middle-income group, where buyers are able to purchase leasehold double-storey homes for less than the RM500,000 mark.

The Building will also have integrated panic buttons for emergencies.

In terms of transportation, there are a myriad of highways that residents can get to quickly and conveniently. The ShahAlam Expressway (KESAS) is nearby as is the Damansara-Puchong Highway (LDP). By utilizing these roads, getting to Bandar Sunway and Shah Alam is very convenient.The closest LRT train station is only 10 minutes away from Sky Condominium, and bus and taxi terminals are only 5minutes away.                                     Kota Kemuning Bayu 2 Storey 24x75 Nice House,Well Maintain,Move-in condition For 850K/Please Call Raymond Cheah 012-6897155 


Kemuning Bayu is an affluent freehold neighbourhood in the township of Kemuning Utama, Shah Alam Selangor. Kemuning Bayu is one of the largest precincts within this township with some 879 residential units. These freehold double-storey terrace houses are built by its developer Paramount Property, a diversified listed Malaysian conglomerate. Kemuning Bayu neighbors the equally affluent Kota Kemuning township. This gated and guarded neighborhood is a highly popular residential development as it offers easy access to major highways.

Kemuning Bayu is a well-planned neighborhood offering ample outdoor facilities and promotes outdoor activities.
Kemuning Bayu Accessibility And Amenities
One advantage of Kemuning Bayu is that is easily accessible via the Shah Alam Expressway (KESAS), Kemuning-Shah Alam Expressway and ELITE Highway making travel hassle-free. There are also buses and taxis that you can take to reach Kemuning Bayu.

A host of amenities nearby Kemuning Bayu are available for residents conveniences such as SJK (T ) Taman Ladang Emerald, SJK (C ) Khe Beng and SK Bukit Kemuning within close proximity whilst for groceries and fresh produce residents can head to Econsave, Pasar Tani Kota Kemuning, Yeon Market Enterprise and Giant Kemuning Utama. For shopping the nearest mall would be neighbouring Gamuda Walk Mall, further away there is Main Place Mall, One City Mall, Setia City Mall and SACC Mall, amongst others. For medical emergencies, Columbia Hospital Bukit Rimau is just a short drive away. Residents would not have to go too far for food as there are plenty of options within close distance of their residences, Bigg Boss Curry House, Selasih Kasturi, Bean Garden and Restaurant KK Corner are some of them.
